when we're in 'em because...

23:23.903 --> 23:26.739
well, we're too busy
looking forward.

23:28.140 --> 23:30.643
But then we spend
the rest of our lives

23:30.677 --> 23:32.745
looking back.

23:34.481 --> 23:36.516
Trying to,
trying to remember them.

23:38.350 --> 23:40.653
