not as fraught.

27:26.846 --> 27:29.115
But it's just...

27:29.148 --> 27:31.150
unconditional.

27:31.183 --> 27:33.886
Easy, pure love.

27:33.920 --> 27:36.956
What an unusual thing.

27:36.989 --> 27:39.458
