-How do you do that?

33:57.203 --> 33:59.071
Bug, come on, come on,
tell us how you do that.

33:59.105 --> 34:00.606
JACK:
It's crazy.

34:00.639 --> 34:02.441
Before you put the blindfold on,

34:02.474 --> 34:04.276
I look to see
where you guys all are.

34:04.310 --> 34:06.112
And you never shut up.

34:06.145 --> 34:09.115
So as long as I know
where you are,

34:09.148 --> 34:11.217
I always know where I'm going.

34:13.319 --> 34:15.387
Baby girl.

34:21.627 --> 34:23.595
-KATE: Hey.
-Hey.

34:29.168 --> 34:31.170
(Kevin exhales)

34:35.407 --> 34:36.775
KEVIN:
You have
a creepy glow about you.

34:36.808 --> 34:38.043
(laughs)

34:38.076 --> 34:40.779
I got some good news.

34:40.812 --> 34:43.048
I got some very good news

34:43.081 --> 34:45.184
on a very sad day.

34:50.189 --> 34:52.758
(sighs)

34:54.160 --> 34:56.462
We don't have parents anymore.

34:56.495 --> 34:58.564
We still have parents.

34:58.597 --> 35:00.832
You know what I mean, though.

35:00.866 --> 35:03.469
Yeah.

35:03.502 --> 35:05.537
What are we gonna do now?

35:07.606 --> 35:09.708
Like, with our lives?

35:12.478 --> 35:15.113
We're gonna do
what she wanted us to do.

35:15.147 --> 35:17.183
We're gonna live fearlessly.

35:19.117 --> 35:21.153
I'm gonna open up
so many music schools

35:21.187 --> 35:22.821
for the visually impaired
that...

35:22.854 --> 35:25.424
People are gonna start becoming
resentful of blind musicians?

35:25.457 --> 35:26.992
-Exactly.
-Yes.

35:27.025 --> 35:29.127
They're gonna say,
"They have it too good."

35:29.161 --> 35:31.163
(all laugh)

35:33.399 --> 35:36.502
I'm gonna focus
on the nonprofit.

35:38.003 --> 35:39.771
Be home more.

35:39.805 --> 35:41.840
I like my home.

35:42.908 --> 35:45.177
Took me a long time to get it.

35:50.749 --> 35:53.619
DNC wants me to go
to the Iowa state fair.

35:53.652 --> 35:56.488
Shake some hands,
eat some junk food.

35:56.522 --> 35:59.325
Deep-fried Oreos and whatnot.

35:59.358 --> 36:01.360
And, uh...

36:01.393 --> 36:04.363
if the folks who like to
deep-fry their food like you...

36:05.597 --> 36:07.165
...then maybe...

36:09.335 --> 36:11.203
You gonna go?

36:11.237 --> 36:13.071
-I'm weighing it with Beth.
-Mm-hmm.

36:13.104 --> 36:14.940
But, uh, if she's down?

36:17.008 --> 36:19.010
For Mom?

36:20.346 --> 36:23.181
Yeah, for Mom I might go.

36:25.116 --> 36:27.353
(Kate laughs)

36:30.589 --> 36:33.024
Can I tell you guys
my nightmare?

36:36.127 --> 36:38.196
We drift.

36:38.230 --> 36:40.599
With Mom being gone
and our busy lives,

36:40.632 --> 36:42.067
we drift.

36:42.100 --> 36:43.435
And I'm not saying we wind up,

36:43.469 --> 36:44.936
you know,
estranged or anything, but...

36:44.970 --> 36:47.673
We're not gonna drift.

36:47.706 --> 36:50.242
We could drift.

36:58.617 --> 37:01.086
Secret.
(clears throat)

37:01.119 --> 37:03.889
If someone asks me
to close my eyes

37:03.922 --> 37:06.625
and picture my family...

37:06.658 --> 37:09.595
it's not Beth and the girls
I see first.

37:10.996 --> 37:13.131
My first picture is Mom and Dad

37:13.164 --> 37:15.267
and the two of you.

37:17.235 --> 37:20.606
Younger, cuter versions
of you two, but still...

37:21.607 --> 37:24.443
-Same.
-Same.

37:27.646 --> 37:29.648
Guys?

37:31.817 --> 37:33.852
First came?

37:36.288 --> 37:38.123
Me.

37:38.156 --> 37:40.826
-And Dad said?
-Gee.

37:40.859 --> 37:43.261
-And then came?
-Me.

37:43.295 --> 37:45.163
-And Mom said?
-We.

37:45.196 --> 37:46.798
-(chuckles)
-And then came?

37:46.832 --> 37:48.867
Me.

37:49.835 --> 37:51.437
And they said?

37:51.470 --> 37:53.672
That's three.

37:53.705 --> 37:55.607
ALL:
Big Three.

37:57.376 --> 37:59.511
Big Three.

38:05.016 --> 38:07.319
(sighs)

38:09.855 --> 38:11.890
Hey, Kate?

38:14.360 --> 38:17.262
If you drifted...

38:17.295 --> 38:19.731
we'd drift right after you.

38:21.132 --> 38:23.168
Aw.

38:25.236 --> 38:27.038
Can you really drift,
though, Kev?

38:27.072 --> 38:28.707
'Cause I can't remember

38:28.740 --> 38:30.275
if you ever actually
learned how to swim.

38:30.308 --> 38:31.810
(both laugh)

38:31.843 --> 38:33.779
Yeah, well,
I had to learn how to swim.

38:33.812 --> 38:35.547
Growing up with you, all those
tears, I would've drowned.

38:35.581 --> 38:37.649
-Right in the kitchen.
-I'm sorry, I'm just in touch

38:37.683 --> 38:39.451
-with my emotions
unlike some people, Robo-Kev.
-Yeah, I'm just saying,

38:39.485 --> 38:41.653
you know, people don't like
their presidents all weepy

38:41.687 --> 38:44.055
and stuff, you know what I mean,
you got to button that up.

38:48.093 --> 38:50.962
She grabbed my hand.

38:50.996 --> 38:53.031
Hard.

38:53.064 --> 38:54.966
Right at the very end.

38:55.000 --> 38:57.035
You know, right before...

38:58.336 --> 38:59.871
Yeah.

38:59.905 --> 39:01.840
I know, I saw.

39:02.841 --> 39:04.843
I wonder what that was.

39:07.045 --> 39:09.080
(train rattling)

39:16.455 --> 39:18.056
Hey.

39:19.224 --> 39:21.527
Hey.

39:26.131 --> 39:27.566
Mm.

39:32.804 --> 39:35.040
I've missed that little scar.

39:36.207 --> 39:38.276
Come on, you didn't even
notice it for over a decade.

39:38.309 --> 39:41.747
Was too busy looking
at the rest of the face.

39:48.319 --> 39:50.556
I'm scared.

39:50.589 --> 39:52.958
I know.

39:52.991 --> 39:55.761
But don't be.

39:57.729 --> 39:59.698
KEVIN:
Okay.

39:59.731 --> 40:01.700
Let's be honest,
now that I'm shaving,

40:01.733 --> 40:03.735
do I seem more like a man?

40:03.769 --> 40:05.804
-No.
-More like Dad?

40:05.837 --> 40:07.639
-You're getting there.
-I don't know, Kev.

40:07.673 --> 40:09.240
I don't,
I don't really see it yet.

40:09.274 --> 40:11.777
You do know how much
I love you, right, Bec?

40:11.810 --> 40:13.111
Babe?

40:13.144 --> 40:14.446
-JACK: Bec?
-REBECCA: Who, me?

40:14.480 --> 40:16.247
Babe, do you, do you know
how much I love you?

40:16.281 --> 40:18.917
You got, you got to appreciate
the little things, Bec.

40:18.950 --> 40:20.118
Babe, you have said that before.

40:20.151 --> 40:21.453
He was, he was listening
to what I said.

40:21.487 --> 40:23.421
He says it all the time.

40:23.455 --> 40:25.624
-Those are big things...
-No, the little things...

40:25.657 --> 40:27.959
(all clamoring)

40:27.993 --> 40:30.295
-Hey, babe?
-Yeah.

40:30.328 --> 40:32.664
We did good.

40:32.698 --> 40:34.600
You...

40:34.633 --> 40:36.668
did so good.

40:38.504 --> 40:41.006
There was so much left
I wanted to do with them.

40:41.039 --> 40:42.974
You will.

40:43.008 --> 40:45.410
All right, go easy on me.
Oh, boy.

40:45.443 --> 40:48.246
Oh... boy.

40:48.279 --> 40:50.682
(all chatting, clamoring)

40:50.716 --> 40:52.818
What?

40:52.851 --> 40:55.621
It's hard to explain,

40:55.654 --> 40:57.122
but...

40:57.155 --> 40:59.525
you'll do all those things
with them.

40:59.558 --> 41:01.493
*

41:03.729 --> 41:05.597
REBECCA:
Promise?

41:05.631 --> 41:07.599
I do.

41:07.633 --> 41:10.101
I mean, it's not
like I want to be there

41:10.135 --> 41:11.870
for anything weird.

41:11.903 --> 41:14.439
I don't want to watch them
shower or anything.

41:14.472 --> 41:15.974
You won't.

41:16.007 --> 41:17.743
But you'll be there.

41:24.082 --> 41:26.151
*

41:28.353 --> 41:30.656
OTHERS:
Oh!

41:32.524 --> 41:33.959
(all clamoring, laughing)

41:33.992 --> 41:35.827
Oh!

41:35.861 --> 41:37.629
I can't dance.

41:37.663 --> 41:39.197
Just focus on the kids.
No, no, no,

41:39.230 --> 41:40.699
no, no, no, no,
no, no, no, no, no.

41:40.732 --> 41:42.133
No! No! No! No! No! No!

41:42.167 --> 41:44.636
(laughing, clamoring)

41:44.670 --> 41:46.738
Quite a thing, isn't it?

41:47.939 --> 41:49.875
Us...

41:49.908 --> 41:52.277
finding each other
in that bar that night.

41:53.244 --> 41:55.647
I don't know.

41:55.681 --> 41:57.683
I mean, when the world

41:57.716 --> 42:00.085
puts something that obvious
in front of you,

42:00.118 --> 42:02.487
you don't just walk away.

42:02.520 --> 42:04.556
*

42:05.791 --> 42:08.026
(laughing, clamoring)

42:10.028 --> 42:12.330
Get Randall!
Get Randall! Get Randall!

42:12.363 --> 42:13.932
(Randall shouting)

42:13.965 --> 42:15.533
JACK:
You ready?

42:17.803 --> 42:19.871
I don't want to leave them.

42:19.905 --> 42:22.040
You don't.

42:22.073 --> 42:24.542
You'll see.

42:26.745 --> 42:29.047
I love you.

42:30.248 --> 42:32.283
I love you.

42:42.293 --> 42:52.337
*

42:52.337 --> 43:02.347
*

